  "title": "Marketing Crew (Training Provided)",
  "description": "<p>Looking for a role that’s people-facing, fast-moving, and actually teaches you real-world skills?</p><p><br /></p><p>We’re expanding our Marketing team and looking for driven individuals to help grow our clients’ brand presence and customer base through on-ground event campaigns across Singapore.</p><p><br /></p><p>This role is ideal if you enjoy interacting with people, want hands-on exposure, and are looking for clear growth instead of a stagnant desk job.</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>What You’ll Be Doing</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><ul><li>Represent well-known brands at event sites and marketing campaigns</li><li>Engage customers and communicate brand messages confidently</li><li>Work closely with a supportive team to execute campaigns smoothly</li><li>Learn how marketing strategies are planned, executed, and scaled</li><li>Take on leadership responsibilities as you grow</li></ul><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>What We Offer</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><ul><li>1-on-1 mentorship & coaching (you won’t be left alone to “figure it out”)</li><li>Structured training provided — no experience required</li><li>Clear progression pathway with fast-tracked advancement</li><li>Opportunities to coach and lead newcomers</li><li>Overseas exposure & travel opportunities</li><li>Energetic team culture with strong support system</li></ul><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>What We’re Looking For</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><ul><li>Open-minded and willing to learn</li><li>Comfortable interacting with people</li><li>Good communication skills (or willing to improve)</li><li>Background in Sales/Marketing is a bonus, but not required</li></ul><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>📍 Work Location: In person (Singapore)</p><p>🕒 Job Type: Full-time</p><p>🎓 Training Provided | Growth-Focused | Performance-Based Progression</p><p><br /></p><p>If you’re curious about how marketing works beyond theory and want a role with real development and momentum, we’d love to meet you</p>",
